{"type": "article", "id": 26970, "title": "大理石花器", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-18T07:23:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134201PT9YEDyRQdjWiFsn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>利用不同材质，伦敦的 <a href=\"http://www.ahsayane.com/\">Ahsayane Studio</a> 通过这个名为 <a href=\"http://www.ahsayane.com/portfolio_page/angel-vase/\">Angel</a> 的定制花器，将极简与美感结合在了一起。每一个花器都经由西班牙石匠手工打造而成，中间留空的部分可以放入圆柱形的黄铜器具，它的纤细感与大理石形成了巧妙的反差，为整体造型增色不少。你可以通过<a href=\"http://angelvase.bigcartel.com/\">链接</a>订购这款花瓶，售价为 695 英镑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134159dfl48aZ0iLvwgSKO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.93833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342005GlifrmEI1wRgaZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134200xJ4pHzRlIV1EZcuX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342018l06Be2jnJ9YC1ZM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}